spell_list.description: Ballad of Warding improves the ward protection granted by Enhance: Elemental Concerto and Enhance: Arcane Symphony. In addition, the final rank grants Elemental Concerto a small chance to cure Elemental when damaged by an Elemental effect and a small chance for Arcane Concerto to cure Arcane when damaged with an Arcane effect.
